item.title: About
item.description: Credits First This site was inspired by the ASA Committee on Career Development Portfolio Project written in Amstat news June 2022. Source codeand method follows the fantastic tutorial bookdown by Yihui Xie, Amber Thomas, Alison Presmanes Hill (2022-08-08). Icon sources: Logo Home from freepnglogos.com 512x512 Logo from freepnglogos.com Linkedin Logo from freepnglogos.com Details This site is built using R language blogdown package and hosted from Netlify connected to my github source code.
